API Endpoints:

todo: User Registration: POST /auth/register
    returns: success message string or error message string

todo: Admin Registration: POST /auth/admin/register
    returns: success message string or error message string

todo: Check Username Availability: GET /auth/check-username/{username}
    returns: true or false

todo: Login: POST /auth/login
    returns: token string or error message string

todo: Create Wallet: POST /wallet/create
    returns: success message string or error message string

todo: Wallet TOTP Creation: POST /wallet/{WalletId}/totp
    returns: QR Code Data URI or error message string

todo: Wallet TOTP Confirmation: POST /wallet/{WalletId}/totp/confirm
    onError: delete secret from wallet
    returns: success message string or error message string

todo: Recharge Wallet: POST /recharge
    returns: success message string or error message string

todo: Transaction Init: POST /transaction/init
    verify the receiver wallet & sender's balance
    returns: Transaction ID or error message string

todo: Transaction Confirm: POST /transaction/confirm
    verify TOTP or OTP & debit & credit the wallets
    returns: success message string or error message string

Wallet Balance: GET /wallet/balance
    returns: balance or error message string

View Account Statement: GET /wallet/statement
    returns: statement or error message string